Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They learned about the ruler of \NPunk Hazard - Caesar's motive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with their pirate ally \N- the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are on the move to kidnap Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save the children, and \Nescape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can! But I'm protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! The Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have balls to \Npick a fight with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't think so! If you wanna run, do it now!\N--A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...picking fights all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Surprising Outcome! \NWhite Chase vs. Vergo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Were you even listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have that crazy pirate backing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Seven Warlords \N- Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the behind-the-scenes \Nstring-puller of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small arms, war weapons, drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's involved in every risky transaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the mastermind of the underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's connected to all the notorious figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll bring you under in a matter of minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can still spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-If you apologize now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about how many monsters you will
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Npiss off if you do something to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?! Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the Warlords \Nand the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll make you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...drown at sea in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you apologize now, I'll \Nlet you off the hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastille!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gas burner attack that could melt iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get melted away? Or incinerated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I know! It doesn't feel \Nlike it's real, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for a rookie who \Njust came to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of those monsters is here in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can compete against his Armament Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker and Law are goners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are all of your crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I said you're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-So why don't you listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you screw with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too weak. You can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My basic fighting skill and \NHaki are better than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:08:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep on fighting because you're
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,angry at me for betraying the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to settle the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish you off with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Haki isn't good enough to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinokuni is a lethal gas that petrifies \Nhuman bodies and kills them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it is now flowing into the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should've been caught \Nup with the kids by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're wounded - shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you mess up something this simple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kids! Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel dizzy. It feels \Nlike I've been dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because of the sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're harmless so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Keep your eyes on the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be alright soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Get it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors are heading \Ntoward R Building, 1st floor -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the location of the last exit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ground zero of the fight \Nbetween Luffy and Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Kin'emon is looking \Nfor his son Momonosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?! Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Momonosuke turned to a small dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't tell anybody but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sliced up Momonosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done a terrible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon-san, you can't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That area is filled up with the gas by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadly gas is right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit will carry me through anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's fire or gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible! Kin'emon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Prism Stone handcuffs... \NMaybe, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I hear the "Usopp \Nalarm" ringing in my head now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's just pretend \Nthat I checked this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them "I looked all over but \Nthe Sea Prism Handcuffs weren't..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...in that room!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this always happening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied now, Smoker-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how deeply you believe in justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do anything if you're weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can take my heart back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kick your ass easily, Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself, squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vergo-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi, I want you to lead the G-5 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Smoker-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going after Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The law can't settle these matters, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it myself! He was \Nmessing around with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you rather die than \Ngrovel before a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to beg for our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,throwing ourselves at his \Nfeet if that's what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if we die here, \Nwe can't save our people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die here, too, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still wanna fight, Smoker-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't turn to \Nsmoke and spread yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thin when you're facing a better Haki user.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just makes it easier for me to hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep using \Nyour Devil Fruit power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even think straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you, Smoker-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you wanna kill me \Nfor messing with the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to be strong \Nenough to do so, Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just reckless, you can't \Nmake your people proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker, my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for winning it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it makes sense! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:18:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you turned to smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just finish him off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna owe a pirate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dishonor to a Navy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too ashamed to be seen by my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was just the help I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo... -san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you remember that I'm better than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to keep thinking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't stay sitting \Non that "throne" forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're listening, "Joker"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo is a dead man, Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to lose your right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Straw Hat-ya will take care of Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're also gonna lose SAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't see this coming \Nbecause you were overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you just keep \Ncackling like always
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and think about your next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't be laughing for long because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're gonna do the unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try acting strong, squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure you'll survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Vergo in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you piss him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pissed Vergo off and then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been traumatic. \NYou probably can't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be afraid of Vergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your incomparable swordplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his Haki will allow him to \Nblock your every attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both in terms of status and power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're no match for Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since \Nthe War of the Best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone actually accomplish anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you did was stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Whitebeard did was end the era.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy Headquarters rounded up new forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The big-timers didn't take any action!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like everybody was \Njust preparing for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That war was only a beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the new era of the daring ones
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is coming along with an unstoppable swell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke... the gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law's attack turns the tables in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats scramble \Nand aim for a quick getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Caesar, at the pinnacle of his rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unleashes a terrible attack on Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that annihilates friend and foe alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Caesar's Defeat!-- The \NPowerful Grizzly Magnum!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
